Symbol.Script_3D:
! Design Sofa 02
if gs_detlevel_3D_m=0 then end
IF GLOB_CONTEXT>20 and GLOB_CONTEXT<40 THEN gs_detlevel_3D_m=1
IF not(gs_shadow) THEN SHADOW OFF
unID=1
!!! *** X Dimension HOTSPOT 0,0,0,unID, A,1+256 : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT -1,0,0,unID, A,3 : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT A,0,0,unID, A,2 : unID=unID+1
HOTSPOT 0,B,0,unID, A,1+256 : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT -1,B,0,unID, A,3 : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT A,B,0,unID, A,2 : unID=unID+1
!!! *** X Dimension HOTSPOT 0,0,0,unID, B,1+256 : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT 0,-1,0,unID, B,3 : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT 0,B,0,unID, B,2 : unID=unID+1
HOTSPOT A,0,0,unID, B,1+256 : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT A,-1,0,unID, B,3 : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT A,B,0,unID, B,2 : unID=unID+1
ADD a/2,b/2,0
hotspot a/2, b/2, 0, unID, zzyzx, 1+128: unID=unID+1 hotspot a/2, b/2, -1, unID, zzyzx, 3: unID=unID+1 hotspot a/2, b/2, zzyzx, unID, zzyzx, 2: unID=unID+1
hotspot -a/2, b/2, 0, unID, zzyzx, 1+128: unID=unID+1 hotspot -a/2, b/2, -1, unID, zzyzx, 3: unID=unID+1 hotspot -a/2, b/2, zzyzx, unID, zzyzx, 2: unID=unID+1
xx=0.035 yy=0.03
! Hotspot editing ! DETAILED 3D IF gs_full_edit=1 THEN hotspot -a/2+0.15+xx, -b/2+yy, 0, unID, gs_seat_height, 1+128: unID=unID+1 hotspot -a/2+0.15+xx, -b/2+yy, -1, unID, gs_seat_height, 3: unID=unID+1 hotspot -a/2+0.15+xx, -b/2+yy, gs_seat_height, unID, gs_seat_height, 2: unID=unID+1
hotspot a/2-0.15-xx, -b/2+yy, 0, unID, gs_seat_height, 1+128: unID=unID+1 hotspot a/2-0.15-xx, -b/2+yy, -1, unID, gs_seat_height, 3: unID=unID+1 hotspot a/2-0.15-xx, -b/2+yy, gs_seat_height, unID, gs_seat_height, 2: unID=unID+1 ENDIF
pen gs_cont_pen SET MATERIAL gs_frame_mat
ADD -a/2,-b/2,0
IF gs_detlevel_3D_m=1 THEN MATERIAL gs_seat_mat
PRISM_ 9,zzyzx, 0,0,15, 0.185,0,15, 0.185,b-0.1,15, a-0.185,b-0.1,15, a-0.185,0,15, a,0,15, a,b,15, 0,b,15, 0,0,-1
PRISM_ 5,gs_seat_height, 0.185,0.03,15, a-0.185,0.03,15, a-0.185,b-0.1,15, 0.185,b-0.1,15, 0.185,0.03,-1 DEL 1 END ENDIF
RESOL gs_resol
!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!! !!!!!!!!!!!!! ***** main legs ***** !!!!!!!!!!!!! !!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!
for i1=1 to 2 ADD 0.0875,0.0125,0 EXTRUDE 2,0,0,zzyzx-0.15-0.05,1+4+16, 0,0,901, 0.0125,360,4001
ADDZ zzyzx-0.15-0.05 ROTZ 180 ADDX 0.0375 ROTZ 90 REVOLVE 2,90,8, 0,0.0375,901, 0.0125,360,4001 del 2
ADD 0.0375, 0, 0.0375 ROTY 90 ROTZ -90 ADDx 0.0375 ROTZ 90 REVOLVE 2,90,8, 0,0.0375,901, 0.0125,360,4001 del 2
ADD 0.0375, 0, 0.0375 ROTY 90 EXTRUDE 2,0,0,b-0.1,4, 0,0,901, 0.0125,360,4001
ADDZ b-0.1
ADDx 0.0375 ROTZ 90 REVOLVE 2,90,1+2+4+8, 0,0.0375,901, 0.0125,360,4001 del 2 del 9 mulx -1 addx -a next i1 del 4
ADD 0.05, b-0.0125,zzyzx-0.15-0.0125 ROTY 90 EXTRUDE 2,0,0,a-0.1,4, 0,0,901, 0.0125,360,4001 del 2
!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!! !!!!!!!!!!!!!! ***** back legs ***** !!!!!!!!!!!!! !!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!
ADD 0.025+0.005+0.15, b-0.0125, 0
addz zzyzx-0.15-0.0125 roty 90 ARMC 0.0125,0.0125,zzyzx-0.15-0.0125,0,0,90 del 2 ADDX a-2*(0.025+0.005+0.15)
addz zzyzx-0.15-0.0125 roty 90 ARMC 0.0125,0.0125,zzyzx-0.15-0.0125,0,0,90 del 2
del 2
!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!! !!!!!!!!!!!!!! ***** skinny bit ***** !!!!!!!!!!!!! !!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!
for i2=1 to 2 ADD 0.0875,0.0125,0
ADDZ leg_h+0.2 ROTY -90 EXTRUDE 2,0,0,0.0675,4, 0,0,901, 0.005,360,4001
ADDZ 0.0675 ROTZ 90 ADDx 0.015 ROTZ 90 REVOLVE 2,90,1+2+4+8, 0,0.015,901, 0.005,360,4001 del 2
ADD 0.015, 0, 0.015 ROTY 90 EXTRUDE 2,0,0,b-0.06,4, 0,0,901, 0.005,360,4001
ADDZ b-0.06
ADDx 0.015 ROTZ 90 REVOLVE 2,90,1+2+4+8, 0,0.015,901, 0.005,360,4001 del 2 del 8
mulx -1 addx -a next i2 del 4
ADD 0.02, b-0.0175, leg_h+0.2 ROTY 90 EXTRUDE 2,0,0,a-0.04,4, 0,0,901, 0.005,360,4001 del 2
!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!! !!!!!!!!!!!!! ***** angled bottom bit ***** !!!!!!!!!!!!! !!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!
! angled bottom bit
add 0.025,0.025,leg_h MATERIAL gs_frame_mat PRISM_ 10,0.025, 0,0,15, a-0.05,0,15, a-0.05,b-0.05,15, 0,b-0.05,15, 0,0,-1, 0.005,0.005,15, a-0.05-0.005,0.005,15, a-0.05-0.005,b-0.05-0.005,15, 0.005,b-0.05-0.005,15, 0.005,0.005,-1
del 1
10: !!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!! !!!!!!!!!!!!! ***** cushions ***** !!!!!!!!!!!!! !!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!
! cushions
ADD 0.03,0.025,leg_h
ROTY -90 ADD 0, 0.005,- 0.15 CALL "fa_cushion_CSo_WMCC" parameters gs_detlevel_3D_m=gs_detlevel_3D_m,cush_a=zzyzx-leg_h, cush_b=b-0.06,cush_h=0.15,r1=0.02,r2=0.02,gs_resol=gs_resol,cush_mat=gs_seat_mat DEL 2
ADD 0.155, b-0.055, 0 ROTX 90 CALL "fa_cushion_CSo_WMCC" parameters gs_detlevel_3D_m=gs_detlevel_3D_m,cush_a=(a-0.06-2*0.15-2*0.005)/2-0.0025, cush_b=zzyzx-leg_h,cush_h=0.1,r1=0.02,r2=0.02,gs_resol=gs_resol,cush_mat=gs_seat_mat ADDX (a-0.06-2*0.15-2*0.005)/2+0.0025 CALL "fa_cushion_CSo_WMCC" parameters gs_detlevel_3D_m=gs_detlevel_3D_m,cush_a=(a-0.06-2*0.15-2*0.005)/2-0.0025, cush_b=zzyzx-leg_h,cush_h=0.1,r1=0.02,r2=0.02,gs_resol=gs_resol,cush_mat=gs_seat_mat DEL 3
ADD a-0.06,0.005,0 ROTY -90 CALL "fa_cushion_CSo_WMCC" parameters gs_detlevel_3D_m=gs_detlevel_3D_m,cush_a=zzyzx-leg_h, cush_b=b-0.06,cush_h=0.15,r1=0.02,r2=0.02,gs_resol=gs_resol,cush_mat=gs_seat_mat DEL 2
ADD 0.155,0.005,0 CALL "fa_cushion_CSo_WMCC" parameters gs_detlevel_3D_m=gs_detlevel_3D_m,cush_a=(a-0.06-2*0.15-2*0.005)/2-0.0025, cush_b=b-2*0.03-0.1-0.005,cush_h=gs_seat_height-leg_h-0.15,r1=0.02,r2=0.02,gs_resol=gs_resol,cush_mat=gs_seat_mat ADDX (a-0.06-2*0.15-2*0.005)/2+0.0025 CALL "fa_cushion_CSo_WMCC" parameters gs_detlevel_3D_m=gs_detlevel_3D_m,cush_a=(a-0.06-2*0.15-2*0.005)/2-0.0025, cush_b=b-2*0.03-0.1-0.005,cush_h=gs_seat_height-leg_h-0.15,r1=0.02,r2=0.02,gs_resol=gs_resol,cush_mat=gs_seat_mat DEL 1
ADDZ gs_seat_height-leg_h-0.15 CALL "fa_cushion_CSo_WMCC" parameters gs_detlevel_3D_m=gs_detlevel_3D_m,cush_a=(a-0.06-2*0.15-2*0.005)/2-0.0025, cush_b=b-2*0.03-0.1-0.005,cush_h=0.15,r1=0.02,r2=0.02,gs_resol=gs_resol,cush_mat=gs_seat_mat ADDX (a-0.06-2*0.15-2*0.005)/2+0.0025 CALL "fa_cushion_CSo_WMCC" parameters gs_detlevel_3D_m=gs_detlevel_3D_m,cush_a=(a-0.06-2*0.15-2*0.005)/2-0.0025, cush_b=b-2*0.03-0.1-0.005,cush_h=0.15,r1=0.02,r2=0.02,gs_resol=gs_resol,cush_mat=gs_seat_mat DEL 1 DEL 2
DEL 1 DEL 2
END
Symbol.Script_2D:
PEN gs_cont_pen
! ====================================================================== ! SCALE ! ======================================================================
call "2dDetailLevel_CSo_WMCC" parameters gs_detlevel_2D_m = gs_detlevel_2D_m, returned_parameters det2D
!!! ******************************** 2D SYMBOL
IF det2D = 1 THEN CALL "fa_SofaSymbol_CSo_WMCC" PARAMETERS ALL iSofaSymbolType = SOFASYMBOL_RECTSIMPLE !! 1/200 IF det2D = 2 THEN CALL "fa_SofaSymbol_CSo_WMCC" PARAMETERS ALL iSofaSymbolType = SOFASYMBOL_RECT3 !! 1/100 IF det2D = 4 THEN CALL "fa_SofaSymbol_CSo_WMCC" PARAMETERS ALL !! Symbolic

!!!! *** Symbol
RR=0.03

LINE2 A,0,A-(RR+0.15/2),0 LINE2 A-(RR+0.15/2),0,A-(RR+0.15/2),RR
FILL gs_fill_type POLY2_B 9, 2, gs_fill_pen, gs_back_pen, 0,0,1, 0,B,1, A,B,1, A,0,1, A-(RR+0.15/2),0,1, A-(RR+0.15/2),RR,1, (RR+0.15/2),RR,1, (RR+0.15/2),0,1, 0,0,1
ENDIF
